tweet: Just got locked out of our air bnb in Seattle and some lady walking her dog asked if @boarcrok and I were homeless cause people have been breaking in. We told her what happened and she responds with, “Good. I’d hate to have to call the cops.”  Update : we back inside

Very hard for me to be detached about BnB. It's like my whole career captured in a single issue, full of so many things I love. And of course I want people to enjoy the words as much as the art, because I've always been a writer too. After three days of nerves I need a beer! :-)
I am the captain now. #pirateLife  @andres___camilo @mister_bnb @ Bocachica, Bolivar, Colombia  https://t.co/dt2FdCCCed
